        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>This system ships items taken from Hackmaster Basic. You may use the following keys in an effect talent to replicate some talents from the full game, or to invent your own. Not every talent can be encoded into the game at this time, but support will grow as this system matures. Watch this space for more keys.</p><h2>Priority</h2><p>Priority influences the order at which effects are applied. Unless explicitly specified, priority can be left blank.</p><h2>Global Modifiers</h2><p>The following effect keys globally modify a character's stats. You should set the effect mode to Add for these. The system expects integer values here, except for top and move, which are floating point values (A move of 1.0 equates to a human's movement speed, and a top value of 0.1 would add 10% to that character's pain threshold).</p><table style=\"height:433.333px;border-width:1px;border-spacing:2px\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Key</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Unit</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Description</td></tr></thead><tbody><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.atk</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Attack modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.def</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Defend modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.dmg</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Damage modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.dodge</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Dodge Save modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.dr</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Armor Damage Reduction modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.foa</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Feat of Agility modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.fos</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Feat of Strength modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.hp</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Maximum Hit Point modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.init</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Initiative Bonus modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.kb</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Knockback modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.luck</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Maximum Luck modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.mental</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Mental save modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.morale</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Morale modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.move</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Float</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Movement Rate modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.physical</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Physical save modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.poison</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Poison save modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.reach</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Weapon Reach modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.sp</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Maximum Spell Point modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.spd</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Weapon Speed modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.spdm</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Melee Weapon Speed modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.spdr</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Ranged Weapon Speed modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.top</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Float</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Threshold of Pain modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.trauma</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Trauma save modifier.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">system.bonus.talent.turning</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Integer</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px\">Global Turning save modifier.</td></tr></tbody></table><h2>Default Modifiers</h2><p>The following modifiers override default actor behaviors.</p><table style=\"height:51.9999px;width:100%;border-width:1px;border-spacing:2px\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:34.1969%\">Key</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:9.32642%\">Unit</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:8.60104%\">Default</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:1.0352%\">Mode</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:0.00107274%\">Pri</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:46.8394%\">Description</td></tr></thead><tbody><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:34.1969%\">hackmaster5e.talent.flag.dodge</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:9.32642%\">Boolean</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:8.60104%\">false</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:1.0352%\">Override</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:0.00107274%\">Â </td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:46.8394%\">Specifies if an actor may Dodge.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17.3333px\"><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:34.1969%\">hackmaster5e.talent.die.trauma</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:9.32642%\">String</td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:8.60104%\">d20</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:1.0352%\">Override</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:0.00107274%\">Â </td><td style=\"height:17.3333px;border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:46.8394%\">Specifies which die to use for a Trauma save.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:34.1969%\">hackmaster5e.talent.sfatigue.basespd</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:9.32642%\">Integer</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:8.60104%\">5</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:1.0352%\">Add</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:0.00107274%\">Â </td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:46.8394%\">Modifies Spell Fatigue duration.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:34.1969%\">hackmaster5e.talent.sfatigue.def</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:9.32642%\">Integer</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:8.60104%\">-6</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:1.0352%\">Add</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:0.00107274%\">-1</td><td style=\"border-width:1px;padding:2px;width:46.8394%\">Modifies Spell Fatigue defense penalty.</td></tr></tbody></table>",
